snippet.title: Quick First Look at RoboSquare Gameplay
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1427760/RoboSquare/
This is Alpha gameplay, recorded while testing with a small group, and wanted others to see what the game looks like, there will be more in-depth trailers later. For now, enjoy a quick sneak peek at RoboSquare coming soon on Steam!

Join the discord to get updates, and when the game becomes available on the Steam store page
https://discord.gg/cdSTbrM
Make by Fizzostia
